text:
MYTHBUSTER:
Does the new coronavirus affect older 
people, or are younger people also susceptible?
People of all ages can be infected by the new 
coronavirus. Older people, and 
people with pre-existing medical conditions 
appear to be more vulnerable to this virus.
#StayAtHome https://t.co/fMyTMK3SH0
